snippet.title: Twelve Sticks - Release Trailer. (Official Video).
snippet.description:
The Game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3064550/Twelve_Sticks/

Play hide-and-seek with friends online. The game can be played by 2-12 people.

Buy upgrades or simply save your collected points, develop your strategies to outperform the other players.

And of course, get scared, have fun, and enjoy playing Twelve Sticks!

#TwelveSticks #Twelve_Sticks #beshbarmakgames
